[Miscellaneous Codes\1 Round Fights]
author=BigBossman
description=This will show that all Player 1's win markers are lit up & Player 2 won't have any of his markers lit. However, whoever wins the round, wins the match. This can make modes like World Competiton with shorter battles to determine a winner.
patch=1,EE,004B5EFD,extended,00000001

