[Miscellaneous Codes\Player 1 Can Drain All of Player 2's Health (Press Select)]
author=BigBossman
description=Pressing Select at any point in the match or just before "Fight" is said will drain all of Player 2's health & force their character to their game over pose & will end the round.
patch=1,EE,D046DBA2,extended,0000FFFE
patch=1,EE,004D368C,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Player 1 Can Force Player 2 to do their Game Over Pose (Press L3)]
author=BigBossman
description=Pressing L3 will force Player 2's character to do their game over pose (during the continue countdown) mid-match. They will be susceptible to hits while doing this. In addition, if they get knocked down, they won't be able to get back up. If they get knocked out of the ring, if they are KOed, or even if time runs out you can still move around. Be careful not to fall out of the ring if you knock them out of the ring as it will count as a loss against you. See Player 1 Can Revive Player 2 code also.
patch=1,EE,D046DBA2,extended,0000FFFD
patch=1,EE,004D368D,extended,00000001

[Miscellaneous Codes\Player 1 Can Revive Player 2 from their Game Over Pose (Press R3)]
author=BigBossman
description=Pressing R3 after forcing Player 2 to do their game over pose or knocking them down will bring them back to normal from being a depressed door mat that won't fight back. If their health is all gone, if time has run out, or if they have been knocked out of the ring, pressing R3 will also end the round.
patch=1,EE,D046DBA2,extended,0000FFFB
patch=1,EE,004D368D,extended,00000000

